title: G-IP 1: Galaxer Logo Discussion
body:
{Summary/ Plan A}
Should we change the logo? 

{Priority and Curb Appeal}
List milestones in priority
Milestone 1:
Vote 


Abstract, Why, How, When
The logo is iconic, however it might have a bad connotation due to the rug. 
This vote is to decide whether we change the logo , keep it, and if we change it we'll do a community competition.


Team Necessary for Milestone: 
The community

Milestone 2:
IF vote to change, run a Community Logo Competition. 
Time between M1-M2
immediate 
Caveats if no more allowance after M2
Milestone 3:
implement new logo across everything
Time between M2-M3
immediate

Commercialization & Future Proofing Strategy
will bring a better sense of the community



{Manifestations}
bigger community drive

{Funding}
no funding needed

{Your commitment to the Dao}
lifer


I _______________futjr________________ hereby swear to this proposal as being thoughtout, derived from a desire to succeed, and for my fellow players.
